author: Second Wind
description:
This video is brought to you by GameMaker, the free, fast, and easy-to-use 2D game engine that’s helped power modern classics like UFO 50, Antonblast, and Yahtzee’s Starstruck Vagabond – https://opr.as/SecondWind-3

This week on Firelink, KC, Nick, and Marty chat their favorite first games from a developer/studio, and why it's always good for teams to have to chance to iterate and build upon in a sequel.

If you dig the podcast, considering supporting us over at Patreon --  https://www.patreon.com/SecondWindGroup

Check out our excellent selection of merch over at our DFTBA store -- https://store.dftba.com/collections/second-wind
title: Favorite First Games From Developers | Firelink Podcast
